long_description: Flojoy Cloud is still in beta, feel free to try it out and give us feedback!
short_description: The FLOJOY_CLOUD_UPLOAD node takes a DataContainer as input and uploads it to Flojoy Cloud.

parameters.name: measurement_id
parameters.description: The measurement id of the data to be uploaded to Flojoy Cloud.

returns.description: The input DataContainer will be returned as it is.
